#month-banner("Three", "Three", "The Secret Fire and the Mineral Mercury", "The philosophic Mercury distinguished — The autonomous fire within the mineral")

#v(0.8em)

#hm-note[
  Month 3 closes Quarter I. The Secret Fire is the most difficult concept in
  Year Three to explain and the most directly perceptible when genuinely present
  in a preparation. Do not over-describe it — the student who has developed the
  inner flame across two and a half years of practice will recognise it when it
  appears. The primary task of Month 3 is building the conceptual and perceptual
  framework for recognition, not for production. The Secret Fire is never forced.
]

